接口 FsUdpPacket


  • public interface FsUdpPacket
    Represents UDP datagram packet, usually based on DatagramPacket.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 静态方法 实例方法 抽象方法 默认方法

      static FsUdpPacket from(java.net.DatagramPacket packet)
      Returns UDP packet of which content comes from given datagram packet.

      Returns readonly data of this datagram packet.

      Returns header info of this datagram packet.

      • from

        static FsUdpPacket from(java.net.DatagramPacket packet)
        Returns UDP packet of which content comes from given datagram packet.
        参数:
        packet - given packet
        返回:
        UDP packet

      • of

        static FsUdpPacket of(java.nio.ByteBuffer buffer,
                      java.net.InetSocketAddress address)
        Returns UDP header of given buffer and address. The given buffer will be read out by this method.
        参数:
        buffer - given buffer
        address - given address
        返回:
        UDP packet
